# Changelog

All notable changes to the Mudae Harem Sorter will be documented in this file.

## [1.2.0] - 2026-04-06
### Added
- New import option: **"Add new characters to bottom"** – when a list already exists, you now get a choice between "Replace entire list" or "Add new characters to bottom". Only new characters (deduplicated by name) are appended, preserving your current order, locks, and arrangement.
- Auto-clear of the import textarea after successful import (both Replace and Add).
- Toast notifications for clearer feedback on import actions.
- Dedicated section in the Help modal explaining how to import new characters to an existing list.
- Ctrl + Click on any card now copies the character name to clipboard (already present in v1.1test but now documented).

### Fixed
- Help button now works correctly.
- Clear button now fully clears the list and UI.
- Jump to Bottom button now scrolls to the actual bottom of the grid (not the $sm output section).

### Changed
- Version bumped to 1.2.0.
- Help modal updated with new import instructions.

## [1.1test] - 2026-04 (pre-1.2.0)
### Added
- Full save/load system (auto localStorage + manual JSON download/upload + paste import).
- Slim top bar with uniform buttons.
- Fixed sidebars at 775px offset from center.
- Ctrl + Click to copy character name to clipboard.
- Position counters on every card (x/y).
- Note display as green pills under kakera.
- Search bar that supports character and series search.
- Navigation sidebar (To Top, End of Locked, To Bottom, Return to Last Position, Jump to Output).
- Improved $sm command generation with proper $smpos chaining and per-box copy buttons.

### Fixed
- Series detection (DANMACHI special case and long titles).
- Various layout and button alignment issues from earlier iterations.

## [1.0] - Initial Stable Release
### Added
- Core Mudae export parser ($mmak-i-s / $mmaki-s support).
- Drag & drop grid with locked section pinning.
- Per-card controls (↑ ↓ SERIES Lock/Unlock).
- Sorting by Name, Series, Kakera (with reverse on second click).
- Shuffle Unlocked.
- $sm command generation with automatic splitting.
- Help modal with full instructions.
- Basic save system foundation.

---

**Thank you for using Mudae Harem Sorter!**
